nly reflection case, this time on `org.apache.tomcat.util.net.Nio2Endpoint` via `IntrospectionUtils.setProperty(...)`. That’s a narrower, separate path from the modeler work, so I’m adding `allPublicMethods` for `Nio2Endpoint` under the `IntrospectionUtils` condition and then doing one last verification pass.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_134\",\"type\":\"file_change\",\"changes\":[{\"path\":\"/home/mihailo/git/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/8328-9aff027d/metadata/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core/11.0.18/reachability-metadata.json\",\"kind\":\"update\"}],\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_134\",\"type\":\"file_change\",\"changes\":[{\"path\":\"/home/mihailo/git/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/8328-9aff027d/metadata/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core/11.0.18/reachability-metadata.json\",\"kind\":\"update\"}],\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_135\",\"type\":\"agent_message\",\"text\":\"The `Nio2Endpoint` method-query entry is in place. I’m doing one last pinned-GraalVM trace run to see whether the remaining failures have collapsed to non-metadata test behavior or whether there’s still another missing introspection target in this Tomcat path.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_136\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/zsh -lc 'export GRAALVM_HOME=/home/mihailo/git/graal/sdk/latest_graalvm_home JAVA_HOME=/home/mihailo/git/graal/sdk/latest_graalvm_home PATH=/home/mihailo/git/graal/sdk/latest_graalvm_home/bin:$PATH; native-image --version'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_137\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/zsh -lc 'export GRAALVM_HOME=/home/mihailo/git/graal/sdk/latest_graalvm_home JAVA_HOME=/home/mihai