{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_46","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18`. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fkimeta%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-8328-library-update-request-org.apache.tomcat.embed-tomcat-embed-core-11.0.18-98227c44\n\nThe most likely failing stage was late native verification. `stats/org.apache.tomcat.embed/tomcat-embed-core/11.0.18/execution-metrics.json` shows the June 19 run ended in `failure` after 5 iterations with `generated_loc: 0`, `test_file: None`, `metadata_file: None`, and the same start/end commit (`b23c918b7828d1e76db7fbfb0679b244689ff92c`), so automation never converged to a patch even though the preserved dynamic-access report reached 216/432 covered calls (50.00%).\n\nConcrete evidence:\n- `logs/org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18/improve-library-coverage/pi-generation-2026-06-19T12-48-42-024009Z.log` shows the run was working on the active class `org.apache.tomcat.SimpleInstanceManager` while also carrying the reporter-requested Connector property path, but no final diff was preserved.\n- `logs/org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-19T12-48-42-036821Z.log` fails `:nativeTest` with `MissingReflectionRegistrationError` for `org.apache.tomcat.util.modeler.modules.MbeansDescriptorsIntrospectionSource` and `org.apache.catalina.core.StandardContext.setDocBase(String)`, plus `NoSuchMethodException` / `ClassNotFoundException` around `MessageDigestCredentialHandler`, `ContextConfig`, and `X509SubjectDnRetriever`.\n- `logs/org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18/native-test-verify/cycle-0-test-2026-06-19T12-53-45-926565Z.log` gets much further but still leaves `HostConfigTest > deploysDescriptorWarAndDirectoryFromHostAppBase()` failing (25/26 native tests passed).\n- `logs/org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-06-19T12-55-11-017905Z.log` then surfaces a `MissingResourceRegistrationError` for `org/apache/mbeans-descriptors.xml`; the log says matching resource metadata exists but is inactive because its runtime conditions were not satisfied.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `logs/org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-06-19T12-48-42-036821Z.log`\n- `logs/org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18/native-test-verify/cycle-0-test-2026-06-19T12-53-45-926565Z.log`\n- `logs/org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-06-19T12-55-11-017905Z.log`\n- `logs/org.apache.tomcat.embed:tomcat-embed-core:11.0.18/improve-library-coverage/pi-generation-2026-06-19T12-48-42-024009Z.log`\n\nNext steps:\n1. Reproduce from the preserved branch and start with the remaining native `HostConfigTest` failure.\n2. Fix the Tomcat metadata/resource conditions around `org/apache/mbeans-descriptors.xml` and the remaining reflection gaps (`MbeansDescriptorsIntrospectionSource`, `StandardContext.setDocBase`, `MessageDigestCredentialHandler`, `ContextConfig`, `X509SubjectDnRetriever`), then rerun `generateMetadata`, `nativeTest`, and `runNativeTraceImage`.\n3. Once native verification is green, preserve the final diff and rerun the automation."}}
